net.proteusframework.ui.miwt

Class ReflectiveAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.AbstractAction
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.ReflectiveAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, EventListener, Action, ActionListener

    public class ReflectiveAction
extends AbstractAction
    Action implementation that takes an Object and method name to call when the Action is fired. The method must be a no argument method.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
